.","h1Line2":"Three stakeholders.","h1Line3":"One trusted truth.","subtitle":"Pulse AI connects Owners, Consultants, and Contractors around a single source of project truth — documents, decisions, tasks, risks, and AI insights in one operational layer.","ctaPrimary":"Request Demo","ctaSecondary":"See Platform","trustedBy":"Trusted by 50+ UAE construction teams"},"problem":{"eyebrow":"THE PROBLEM","titleLead":"Every stakeholder works from a","titleAccent":"different version","titleTrail":" of the truth.","body":"Drawings in one drive. Decisions in an inbox. Tasks in a spreadsheet. Risks in a slide deck. Multiplied across 3 companies — chaos is inevitable.","card1Title":"Fragmented Reality","card1Body":"Each company maintains its own files, statuses, and numbers. Three companies — three conflicting truths.","card2Title":"Invisible Risk","card2Body":"Critical decisions get buried in email threads and meeting notes. By the time risk surfaces, it is already a crisis.","card3Title":"Costly Rework","card3Body":"Misalignment compounds daily. By the time it surfaces, the budget variance and schedule loss are irreversible.","wireframe":{"owner":"OWNER","consultant":"CONSULTANT","contractor":"CONTRACTOR"}},"rolePerspectives":{"eyebrow":"FOR EVERY ROLE ON THE PROJECT","title1":"Three perspectives.","title2":"One reality.","subtitle":"Each stakeholder sees exactly what they need — no more noise, no missing context. All from one shared project truth.","owner":{"title":"Owner","label":"Executive Control","bullets":["Executive dashboards","Budget & schedule visibility","Board-ready reporting","Decision tracking"],"cta":"Enter Owner Portal","dashboard":{"label":"Al Reem Tower · Owner View","live":"Live","spent":"spent","budget":"Budget","schedule":"Schedule","rfis":"RFIs Open","onTrack":"on track","variance":"variance","pending":"pending","generateReport":"Generate Board Report","pendingCount":"6 pending"}},"consultant":{"title":"Consultant","label":"Review & Compliance","bullets":[